column3: This one greets walking one. Does walking one need something of this one?
This one is called Knolexia. This one is tasked with weaving for the benefit of all these ones.
These ones are skilled at weaving. With needle and thread, these ones can make most anything, even houses!
Walking one notices embroidery on homes? Enchanted patterns for repelling dark things!
This place is called Little Solace, new home of these ones.
These ones used to live happily deep in the wood, but then naughty ones went and summoned a primal one.
Fearing naughty ones who became touched ones, these ones fled the homeland. Thanks to horned one Kan–E, these ones could build a new home here.
This one knows not when, but someday these ones will return home. This one is hopeful!
What kind of place is this?
